This endpoint updates a face by face-id. It detects and adds the biggest face from the image.

<aside class="notice">
The minimum height and width of the face should be 180px.
</aside>

### Request Information
`POST - /api/fr/v1/update_face`

### Headers
|Key|Value|
|-------|--------|
|Content-type|application/json|

### Requests parameters
|Field|Type|Description|
|-------|-------|--------|
|key|string|Customer project authentication|
|id|string|Face-id returned with add_face api|
|image_string| string (base64/url)| Base64/Url string of image containing face you want to update |